Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一冲进去就没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道现在必须要去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了之后自然会找到答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一名火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅只是一个秘器的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星黎殿内的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没布下结界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是应该知道我们会冲入的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星黎殿”内应该有“化装舞会”的徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有燐子的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这里面吧 溢出大量存在之力的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没想隐藏“零时迷子”的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已没有谨慎从事的余地了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就叫夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一人到达“零时迷子”那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必顾虑对方全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的答案...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和这么个大家伙作战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城堡遍布自在式一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊 妨碍实验的不逞之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 万事就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍实验的家伙就得为实验献身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此“灵魂殿堂”的主题“永恒与轮回”作贡献吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是燐子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“追根究底”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之力被吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很正确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸收入侵者的力量以完善防御的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 “追根究底”那家伙耍花招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是轻而易举地让我们进来的原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那些家伙在动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是他设置了特殊措施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贽殿遮那好重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 只能靠习得的体术了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想在“天道宫”时的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕无法后退了 终究还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有去找“零时迷子”了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫大的讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明外面正在漫溢存在之力...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市中洋溢着存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为“零时迷子”的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护城市或许那的确是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅只是秘器而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你进入了我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:11:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你在进入我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的思绪正在充沛我的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为寻求答案 祈祷至今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请你更多地更多地...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赌一下吧 千变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是那个“天壤劫火”和“梦幻冠带”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为容器的火雾战士若是用不了存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟一个凡人没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“灵魂殿堂”就要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之力将永不停歇地增长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那里战斗着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之力开始饱和了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也在你的预料之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为礼炮而言虽然稍微有点过了...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是无人见识过的倾注了过剩的存在之力的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道才要试验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了知道这个世界的真相 法则 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学 由佳里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉形势不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 变成什么样了 这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啓作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:15:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你们有没有听到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啓作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着啊 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士的使命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立马走人的你...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 马上去玻璃坛那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就在玻璃坛边上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要查什么快点说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的牢骚就当没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着“星黎殿”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星黎殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮在空中的那座大城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丫头她们好像冲进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有个奇怪的自在法发动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找找看那个自在式在城堡的哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调教的成果嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得力的手下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是说来就来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动听的乐曲再奏一首
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 动听的乐曲再奏一首
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 你奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 动听的乐曲再奏一首
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击的自在法生成装置...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“悼词诵读者”好像回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 为什么火雾战士要到处破坏新的尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他们潜入的话赫卡特会很生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也得出战了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是被“悼词诵读者”救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这气息...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悖论裁决者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出场了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望别来捣乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做出这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围都是能量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成为孽缘之前做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一个人到达就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案已经有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘器的破坏...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要使世界平衡崩溃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不会让他们得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳 我是“炎发灼眼的讨伐者”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也有称作“夏娜”的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会达成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不想破坏“秘器”悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两者都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论少了哪一个都不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不仅仅是一个火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为“炎发灼眼的夏娜”按自己的理念战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你决定了 那就不用多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所相信的是一个真真切切的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束之后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万状饰者 梦幻冠带
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 转身就逃实在太无情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够陪我好好玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我想把坂井悠二怎么样 希望坂井悠二怎么做是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此就能让我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就叫夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从此刻开始这么称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再只是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼的火雾战士成了夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 因为是夏娜所以救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是夏娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 因为不仅仅只是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将这一点...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把夏娜看成仅仅只是个火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.56,0:22:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 我一定要救出你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼眼的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.30,0:24:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.39,0:24:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲的心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.68,0:24:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女在火焰中笑了
